    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a procedurally generated planet filled with resources to harvest, alone or with friends - with a variety of biomes and creatures to discover. Encounter structures containing potentially rare items, from materials to craft new items, to a brand new piece of armour, or maybe even something to lure evil towards you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323260/extras/f63fbee1feccbf677fefcbd494046e6d.poster.avif?t=1755691262\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323260/extras/f63fbee1feccbf677fefcbd494046e6d.webm?t=1755691262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323260/extras/f63fbee1feccbf677fefcbd494046e6d.mp4?t=1755691262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your base across a walkable seamless planet surface to protect yourself and fight off calamitous beasts - if successful, you may have the ingredients to construct a new weapon!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323260/extras/9473935ea058794f2706e99f5bc0fc1e.poster.avif?t=1755691262\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323260/extras/9473935ea058794f2706e99f5bc0fc1e.webm?t=1755691262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323260/extras/9473935ea058794f2706e99f5bc0fc1e.mp4?t=1755691262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323260/extras/44807612d7a398318be7aa3433d10b4f.poster.avif?t=1755691262\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323260/extras/44807612d7a398318be7aa3433d10b4f.webm?t=1755691262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323260/extras/44807612d7a398318be7aa3433d10b4f.mp4?t=1755691262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the planet's creatures cannot be stopped by your power, assemble a rocket and explore new worlds, or even visit the local space station to engage with the economy or converse with the inhabitants!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323260/extras/09f6f7f1db12167aa0cfcbe1ea25c519.poster.avif?t=1755691262\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323260/extras/09f6f7f1db12167aa0cfcbe1ea25c519.webm?t=1755691262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323260/extras/09f6f7f1db12167aa0cfcbe1ea25c519.mp4?t=1755691262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planeturem's engine is written entirely from scratch in C++, designed from the ground up for the game. This means it will run on pretty much any computer you can find!</p>",
